@NODE previewenglish "RealTimeWatch/Zukunft/english"


It's no fun writing AmigaGuide. Of course I could use "Heddley" - but that's
Shareware and no fun either. It's just a higher level of effort.@{PAR}

That is why I am doing a program now , that allowes interactive Guide-writing,
just like a text editor, but with a user interface that complies to the needs
of AmigaGuide. This is going to be a larger project and will therefore take a
bit more time. I am looking forward to present a working version within this
year (1997 ;^).@{PAR}

@ENDNODE

